,"label":"Singh_2018","identifier":"https://doi.org/10.1136/bjsports-2017-098136","enumerator":"2","key":"ROz26YUATl"},{"type":"text","value":", ","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":1}},"key":"azqDOi17Lg"},{"type":"cite","url":"https://doi.org/10.1007/s10648-020-09585-3","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Camacho-Morles ","key":"hwK7cRigAf"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"et al.","key":"jf25zT9nFg"}],"key":"iPEhlCOpX4"},{"type":"text","value":" (2021)","key":"wiYmfF0nCU"}],"kind":"narrative","label":"Camacho_Morles_2021","identifier":"https://doi.org/10.1007/s10648-020-09585-3","enumerator":"3","key":"kxLdgXuTmF"},{"type":"text","value":").","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":1}},"key":"hz3T8UsxrQ"}],"key":"YXnxtHhO5r"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In some perspectives, a successful study method is investing most of study time per day without any distraction from social activities, gaming or entertainment. Previous study shows that study habits, skills, and attitudes can predict student academic performance, meaning that having serious learning behaviors for everyday plays an important role in grades (","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"Qs7FRqu1PG"},{"type":"cite","url":"https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1745-6924.2008.00089.x","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Credé & Kuncel (2008)","key":"UMEuy6mnMq"}],"kind":"narrative","label":"Cred__2008","identifier":"https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1745-6924.2008.00089.x","enumerator":"4","key":"TvsUhCuPwA"},{"type":"text","value":").","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"wa5vBI6jte"}],"key":"iuV0QeUmyJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"However, nowadays, student life is not just studying. They also spent time socializing and participating in other physical or extracurricular activities. Studying in a strict way might not be the most effective method to acquire high scores. ","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"xEc9BcSF0T"},{"type":"cite","url":"https://doi.org/10.3390/ijerph17165972","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Barbosa ","key":"VegOBypx2i"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"et al.","key":"vxgjvIWSsg"}],"key":"RoThjGkfKW"},{"type":"text","value":" (2020)","key":"aIb3V5RLrE"}],"kind":"narrative","label":"Barbosa_2020","identifier":"https://doi.org/10.3390/ijerph17165972","enumerator":"5","key":"DdClnkSadH"},{"type":"text","value":" found that sports participation may benefit students’ academic achievement. Besides, according to ","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"CPbayXmlFt"},{"type":"cite","url":"https://doi.org/10.1002/pits.10136","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gilman ","key":"yM1ScKdyXj"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"et al.","key":"U4qS2niuBn"}],"key":"PqvUS0NfWz"},{"type":"text","value":" (2003)","key":"AxTltxt2zq"}],"kind":"narrative","label":"Gilman2003Structured","identifier":"https://doi.org/10.1002/pits.10136","enumerator":"6","key":"QSNejCZrh9"},{"type":"text","value":" findings, participating in extracurricular activities in a structured way can also enhance school performance of students.","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"x1thmDM1YP"}],"key":"ENWiDJpDsL"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"typ